name: experiments in network blending video no.1
description: An experiment in network blending using stylegan2 ada pytorch. Thanks to Nvidia, Justin Pinkney, and Derrick Schultz for building the tools to make this possible. [video description: A somewhat abstract flower set of flowers morphs between states. It starts as a solitary clump of red and black flower, then morphs to a sea of off white flowers, then goes to a, before becoming a branch on a yellow ochre background, finally morphing through off white to back where it began. The texturing has a watercolorish nature to it but is distinctly digital.] Created by @duskvirkus
